emical abundance is\ngenerally homogeneous, we also find weak evidence for rapid N pollution by WR\nstellar winds at scales of ~ 200 pc.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 26 Sep 2014 10:26:01 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sun, 9 Nov 2014 10:32:25 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-06-23"}
